{"word":"Scorpion","slug":"scorpion","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Scorpion</b> A venomous insect common in the wilderness through which the children of Israel journeyed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=8&verse=15'>Deu 8:15</a><br/> Power over, given to the seventy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=19'>Luk 10:19</a><br/> Unfit for food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=11&verse=12'>Luk 11:12</a><br/> Sting of, in the tail<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=10'>Rev 9:10</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of enemies<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=2&verse=6'>Eze 2:6</a> <br/> - Of cruelty<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=11'>1Ki 12:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=14'>1Ki 12:14</a> <br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=3'>Rev 9:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=5'>Rev 9:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=10'>Rev 9:10</a>"}]}